    "description": "Write a Python function called `parse_tag_0` that must extract text between <tag0> and </tag0>. Practice string parsing.\nDifficulty: Intermediate.\nExamples:\n  parse_tag_0(\"x<tag0>value</tag0>y\") -> \"value\"\n  parse_tag_0(\"plain\") -> \"\"",
