    "description": "Write a Python function called `accumulate_groups_1` that must group numbers by remainder modulo 2. Practice accumulation pattern.\nDifficulty: Intermediate.\nExamples:\n  accumulate_groups_1([1, 2, 3, 4]) -> {\"0\": [2, 4], \"1\": [1, 3]}\n  accumulate_groups_1([0, -1, 1]) -> {\"0\": [0], \"1\": [-1, 1]}",
